```plantuml
@startuml freenowtech_AndroidCI
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor Developer

rectangle "Jenkins Master" as JenkinsMaster #lightblue {
}

rectangle "Docker Host" as DockerHost #lightgreen {
  rectangle "Jenkins Agent\n(Docker Container)" as JenkinsAgent #lightyellow
  rectangle "Android SDK\n(Docker Image)" as AndroidSDK #aliceblue
}

rectangle "Android Project" as AndroidProject #mistyrose

' ========== Connections ==========
Developer --> JenkinsMaster : trigger build

' Jenkins Master interactions
JenkinsMaster --> DockerHost : schedule build job
JenkinsMaster --> JenkinsAgent : communicate build tasks

' Jenkins Agent interactions
JenkinsAgent --> AndroidSDK : utilize for build & test
JenkinsAgent --> AndroidProject : checkout source code\n execute build & test

' Docker Host interactions
DockerHost --> JenkinsAgent : provision container
DockerHost <--> JenkinsMaster : manage container lifecycle

@enduml
```